      <title>特勤局局长在特朗普遇刺后辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-23/urgent-secret-service-director-steps-down-after-assassination-attempt-against-ex-president-trump-at-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[她面临着强烈的抗议，指责负责保护现任和前任总统的机构未能完成其核心使命。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-23/urgent-secret-service-director-steps-down-after-assassination-attempt-against-ex-president-trump-at-rally</guid>
